<subSubSection id="C89655E1E349805CFF70FE8F4705FDEA" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8033066AE349805CFF70FE8F4705FDEA" blockId="2.[178,1085,367,594]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">
Comment: 
<taxonomicName id="478C7DE9E349805CFEAAFE8F4663FE3D" authorityName="HAYASHI" authorityYear="1994" box="[360,583,367,389]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ishiharai">
<emphasis id="B2F8DA78E349805CFEAAFE8F4663FE3D" box="[360,583,367,389]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">Lathrobium ishiharai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was originally recorded from Honshu (
<collectingCountry id="F89B46FAE349805CFC3BFE8F4011FE3D" box="[1017,1077,367,389]" name="Japan" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">Japan</collectingCountry>
) (
<bibRefCitation id="E41D7B9BE349805CFF7BFE6C4572FE1A" author="HAYASHI Y" box="[185,342,396,418]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" pagination="145 - 149" refId="ref6519" refString="HAYASHI Y. (1994): A new macropterous Lathrobium species from Japan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Transactions of the Shikoku Entomological Society 20 (3 - 4): 145 - 149." type="journal article" year="1994">HAYASHI 1994</bibRefCitation>
). Recently, 
<bibRefCitation id="E41D7B9BE349805CFE0DFE6D464EFE1A" author="RYVKIN A" box="[463,618,396,418]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" pagination="135 - 170" refId="ref6803" refString="RYVKIN A. B. (2011): On new and poorly known Lathrobium (s. str.) species from Siberia and the Russian Far East (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Baltic Journal of Coleopterology 11 (2): 135 - 170." type="journal article" year="2011">RYVKIN (2011)</bibRefCitation>
described a subspecies, 
<taxonomicName id="478C7DE9E349805CFCA4FE6E4013FE1A" authorityName="HAYASHI" authorityYear="1994" box="[870,1079,396,419]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="ishiharai" subSpecies="ursinum">
<emphasis id="B2F8DA78E349805CFCA4FE6E4013FE1A" box="[870,1079,396,419]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">L. ishiharai ursinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, from the Russian Far East. According to 
<bibRefCitation id="E41D7B9BE349805CFDA6FE4B4727FE78" author="RYVKIN A" box="[612,771,426,448]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" pagination="135 - 170" refId="ref6803" refString="RYVKIN A. B. (2011): On new and poorly known Lathrobium (s. str.) species from Siberia and the Russian Far East (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Baltic Journal of Coleopterology 11 (2): 135 - 170." type="journal article" year="2011">RYVKIN (2011)</bibRefCitation>
, who does not state if he had seen material of 
<taxonomicName id="478C7DE9E349805CFEA0FE2845FEFE65" authorityName="HAYASHI" authorityYear="1994" box="[354,474,455,477]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ishiharai">
<emphasis id="B2F8DA78E349805CFEA0FE2845FEFE65" box="[354,474,455,477]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">L. ishiharai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="F89B46FAE349805CFDDCFE28467EFE65" box="[542,602,456,477]" name="Japan" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">Japan</collectingCountry>
, 
<taxonomicName id="478C7DE9E349805CFDA5FE284718FE65" authorityName="HAYASHI" authorityYear="1994" box="[615,828,455,477]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="ishiharai" subSpecies="ursinum">
<emphasis id="B2F8DA78E349805CFDA5FE284718FE65" box="[615,828,455,477]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">L. ishiharai ursinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinguished from 
<taxonomicName id="478C7DE9E349805CFBEAFE284551FE42" authorityName="HAYASHI" authorityYear="1994" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="ishiharai" subSpecies="ishiharai">
<emphasis id="B2F8DA78E349805CFBEAFE284551FE42" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">L. ishiharai ishiharai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by shorter elytra and the slightly differently shaped apex of the aedeagus. The sexual characters of the males in the above material are similar to those illustrated by 
<bibRefCitation id="E41D7B9BE349805CFE85FDC045D3FD8D" author="HAYASHI Y" box="[327,503,543,565]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" pagination="145 - 149" refId="ref6519" refString="HAYASHI Y. (1994): A new macropterous Lathrobium species from Japan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Transactions of the Shikoku Entomological Society 20 (3 - 4): 145 - 149." type="journal article" year="1994">HAYASHI (1994)</bibRefCitation>
. Consequently, zoogeographic evidence would suggest that the subspecific status of 
<taxonomicName id="478C7DE9E349805CFE15FDDD4683FDEA" authorityName="HAYASHI" authorityYear="1994" box="[471,679,572,594]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="ishiharai" subSpecies="ursinum">
<emphasis id="B2F8DA78E349805CFE15FDDD4683FDEA" box="[471,679,572,594]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1645">L. ishiharai ursinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is doubtful.
</paragraph>
